g.text: Manages the specific criteria of the new vaccine
Creates a specific administration process for the new vaccine
After a new vaccine gets it's attributes and administration method it gets saved and registered in the system to be used.
The process of registering a new vaccine was split into two.
If ,in the future, a specific vaccine administration method gets changed
you just need change it on the administration class, without making any changes to the actual vaccine
We used composition because if the AddNewVaccine class gets destroyed
then there will be no vaccine to administer therefore
there will also not be a administration method for a vaccine that does not exist
